summary: Just a collection of morrowind giant mushrooms.
descriptionHtml:
I´m thinking about making a mod near morrowind and made this for it and thought on releasing it as a resource.

NOTE:I don´t want to support steam workshop so do not upload this on steam workshop, if you make a mod that contain this resources and wish to upload your mod on steamworkshop just don´t include this resource files there and instead give the link to this page in the descripton thank you.
